  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Yes, several Indian banks offer personalized gift cards that allow you to add a custom image or design. Here are a few banks known for this feature:\n\n1. **HDFC Bank**: HDFC Bank provides a facility called the \"Gift Card\" that allows customers to design their cards by uploading a personal image.\n\n2. **Axis Bank**: Axis Bank offers personalized gift cards where customers can choose their images, helping to create a unique gift.\n\n3. **ICICI Bank**: ICICI Bank also allows you to personalize their gift cards with images or messages, making them a special gifting option.\n\n4. **Kotak Mahindra Bank**: Kotak offers customizable gift cards as well, where you can select an image or a message.\n\nYou typically need to visit the bank's website or app for specific instructions on how to create these personalized gift cards. Be sure to check the terms and conditions, as there may be limitations on the size and type of images used.",
